quran[10]{c,v,t}:
  27,89,"Man jaa bilhasanatifalahu khayrun minha wahum min fazaAAin yawma-ithinaminoon"
  27,90,"Waman jaa bissayyi-atifakubbat wujoohuhum fee annari hal tujzawna illama kuntum taAAmaloon"
  27,91,"Innama omirtu an aAAbuda rabba hathihialbaldati allathee harramaha walahu kullushay-in waomirtu an akoona mina almuslimeen"
  27,92,"Waan atluwa alqur-ana famani ihtadafa-innama yahtadee linafsihi waman dalla faqulinnama ana mina almunthireen"
  27,93,"Waquli alhamdu lillahisayureekum ayatihi fataAArifoonaha wamarabbuka bighafilin AAamma taAAmaloon"
  28,1,"Ta-seen-meem"
  28,2,"Tilka ayatu alkitabialmubeen"
  28,3,"Natloo AAalayka min naba-i moosawafirAAawna bilhaqqi liqawmin yu/minoon"
  28,4,"Inna firAAawna AAala fee al-ardiwajaAAala ahlaha shiyaAAan yastadAAifu ta-ifatanminhum yuthabbihu abnaahum wayastahyeenisaahum innahu kana mina almufsideen"
  28,5,"Wanureedu an namunna AAala allatheenaistudAAifoo fee al-ardi wanajAAalahum a-immatanwanajAAalahumu alwaritheen"
